{"data": [{"id": "4743355", "title": "OIH: The Pros And Cons Of The Oil Services ETF Product", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Full Shot of Oilfield Worker Using Digital Tablet next to Oil Pump Jack\" data-id=\"2156728724\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"810px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">halbergman/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>On November 5, U.S. voters had an energy policy choice. The outgoing administration supported addressing climate change by continuing the U.S. energy policy to support alternative and renewable fuels and inhibiting the production and consumption of hydrocarbons. The incoming administration</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156728724/image_2156728724.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743355-oih-pros-and-cons-of-oil-services-etf-product", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 20:41:47"}, {"id": "4743352", "title": "Bitcoin ETFs Showdown: Is BITU Worth The Volatility?", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Abstract Bitcoin Cryptocurrency concept\" data-id=\"1368998806\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Olemedia</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This article is part of my \u201cBitcoin ETFs Showdown\u201d series, where I analyze several Bitcoin (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BTC-USD\" title=\"Bitcoin USD\">BTC-USD</a>) ETFs and compare them to the iShares Bitcoin Trust ETF (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IBIT\" title=\"iShares Bitcoin Trust ETF\">IBIT</a>).</p> <p>Today, I will analyze for the first time a leveraged Bitcoin ETF: the ProShares Ultra</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368998806/image_1368998806.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743352-bitcoin-etfs-showdown-bitu-worth-volatility", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 20:34:02"}, {"id": "4743349", "title": "EVG: Not An Attractive Entry Point Anymore For This CEF (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Fixed income concept. Types of investment security that pay investors fixed interest or dividend payments until their maturity date. Finance business conceptual. Money bag.\" data-id=\"1625101509\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"910px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Andrii Yalanskyi</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p>We <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4681105-evg-this-9-percent-yielding-cef-is-finally-attractive\">last covered</a> the Eaton Vance Short Duration Diversified Income Fund (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EVG#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" title=\"Eaton Vance Short Duration Diversified Income Fund\">EVG</a>) in the beginning of the year with a 'Buy' rating. The name has outperformed since, being up over 13% on a total return basis:</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743349-evg-not-an-attractive-entry-point-anymore-for-this-cef", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 20:29:31"}, {"id": "4743342", "title": "MicroStrategy: Risky Business Model Makes It A Top Short Idea For 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321734066/image_1321734066.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bitcoin Conference Draws Cryptocurrency Fans To Miami\" data-id=\"1321734066\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3000px\" height=\"2000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321734066/image_1321734066.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321734066/image_1321734066.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321734066/image_1321734066.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321734066/image_1321734066.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321734066/image_1321734066.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321734066/image_1321734066.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321734066/image_1321734066.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321734066/image_1321734066.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Joe Raedle</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Short Ideas for 2025</h2> <p>There are many potential short ideas for 2025. For example, there is a maturity wall of refinancing in the Commercial Real Estate, which would also negatively affect exposed regional banks (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KRE\" title=\"SPDR S&amp;P Regional Banking ETF\">KRE</a>). The Gen</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321734066/image_1321734066.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743342-microstrategy-risky-business-model-makes-it-a-top-short-idea-for-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 20:19:27"}, {"id": "4743338", "title": "Airbnb: Near-Term Headwinds Clouding The Company's Long-Term Potential", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439680709/image_1439680709.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"House keys against swimming pool\" data-id=\"1439680709\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439680709/image_1439680709.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439680709/image_1439680709.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439680709/image_1439680709.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439680709/image_1439680709.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439680709/image_1439680709.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439680709/image_1439680709.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439680709/image_1439680709.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439680709/image_1439680709.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Despite the strong performance of the business since Airbnb (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ABNB\" title=\"Airbnb, Inc.\">ABNB</a></span>) became a public company, the stock has struggled. This situation has persisted in 2024, with Airbnb's share price remaining volatile without really going anywhere.</p> <p>While Airbnb's current valuation isn't overly</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1439680709/image_1439680709.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743338-airbnb-near-term-headwinds-clouding-the-companys-long-term-potential", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 20:12:30"}, {"id": "4743337", "title": "AutoZone: Stick With This Winning Compounder", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\